Resting a hand lightly on the gun in your holster, you stop walking and turn your head slightly to look at your would-be assailant from the corner of one eye. 
"Can I help you?", Your voice is high pitched and stuttering. Your eyes blink or stray from the target. Whatever he had planned to do, your words seem to have made the man sure he can take you on.
You can see him clearly now. Tall, skinny, dark haired, sunken eye, sallow skin and wielding a steel pipe. His cracked lips move as if trying to speak but no words come out..
Realizing that man may be hostile, you start moving backwards as the man launches at you.
Both you and man rolles on to the stationed train that just opened it doors.#
